## Frontend Routes

Once the backend is running, the UI is available at:

- `/ui` – Home
- `/ui/predict` – Predict page
- `/ui/analytics` – Analytics page
- `/ui/about` – About page
- `/ui/agent` – Agent chat page

FastAPI Swagger docs are typically available at:

- `/docs`

