## Current Focus / MVP Scope

This repository is best understood as an MVP that combines:

- trained forecasting artifacts
- model evaluation access
- lightweight dashboard pages
- a practical AI assistant over forecast data

It is especially useful for demonstrations, academic projects, and decision-support prototypes.

